id: lwip_netif_ppp
label: "PPP"
pretty_name : "LWIP generic network interface device drivers for PPP"
package: platform
description: >
    The lwIP PPP support is based from pppd (http://ppp.samba.org) with
    huge changes to match code size and memory requirements for embedded
    devices. Please read /doc/ppp.txt and ppp/PPPD_FOLLOWUP for a detailed
    explanation.
category: LwIP|netif
quality: production
provides:
  - name: lwip_netif
    allow_multiple: true
  - name: lwip_netif_ppp
requires:
  - name: lwip_core
source:
  - path: util/third_party/lwip/lwip/src/netif/ppp/polarssl/arc4.c
